title: Penta Kill on Teemo

embed.description: Song: [No Copyright Music] Electronic Vibes - HookSounds

body:
This was a pretty interesting game, the score was very close 21 - 22 before the penta kill fight, favouring the enemy team with Yasou mainly carrying them. I kept telling my friend who was playing Khazix not to worry and that we could come back and still win it. 

After winning that team fight we ended up getting baron which helped us gain back map control and the enemy team eventually surrendered. 

End score on Teemo: 14 - 2 - 8

End Team scores: 36 - 30
